`markdown

🧾 Reviewer Quick Reference Card — CrystalCastle

🚀 Deploy Essentials
- ✅ Entry point: index.html (AI Video Studio)
- ⚙️ Config: vercel.json with AI Gateway (Groq, Gemini, OpenAI)
- 🧩 Ignore: vitest.config.js, task.md, tiktok* via .vercelignore
- 📦 Deploy command: vercel deploy --prod --archive=tgz

---

🔍 Governance & Workflow
- Active workflows:
  - ci.yml, reviewer-checklist.yml, auto-apply.yml
  - security-scan.yml, ai-validation.yml
- Archived workflows:
  - release.yml, stale.yml, dispatchflow.yml → workflows/notuse/

---

⚠️ Troubleshooting
- 🕒 Build Timeout → Pre-build locally (npm run build)
- 📁 File Size Error → Compress or host externally
- 🚫 Rate Limit → Reduce deploys / upgrade plan
- 🧠 CI/CD Fail → Fix workflow or remove unused jobs

---

✅ Reviewer Checklist
- [ ] Failover tested (Groq → Gemini → OpenAI)
- [ ] Cache works (TTL 60s)
- [ ] Logs + severity matrix visible
- [ ] Cost tracking enabled
- [ ] Notes bilingual (EN/TH)

---

